headline: Can Zebra (ZBRA) Climb 38.01% to Reach the Level Wall Street Analysts Expect?
summary: The average of price targets set by Wall Street analysts indicates a potential upside of 38% in Zebra (ZBRA). While the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric is questionable, the positive trend in earnings estimate revisions might translate into an upside in the stock.
